tem toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-4-%E5%A3%B0%E9%80%9F%E4%BC%AA%E5%BD%B1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.4 声速伪影</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-5-%E6%97%81%E7%93%A3%E6%A0%85%E7%93%A3%E4%BC%AA%E5%BD%B1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.5 旁瓣栅瓣伪影</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-6-%E6%8E%A5%E8%A7%A6-%E8%80%A6%E5%90%88%E4%BC%AA%E5%BD%B1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.6 接触&#x2F;耦合伪影</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3. 视频资料</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">参考资料</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Landdon","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/45172823/196003286-c2c4aa6e-a365-4492-ac64-aede8e18b244.jpeg","link":"/","description":"保持平和，持续进步 </br> </br> 一起加油！","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"【001】超声成像原理","uid":"d9a732effe27f241e9c05e953952097e","slug":"我的第一篇博客文章","date":"2022-10-15T16:16:45.000Z","updated":"2022-11-03T16:09:15.672Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/我的第一篇博客文章.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/45172823/196041977-f2e095a9-633e-40e9-8f0a-883ee5d05010.png","text":"超声成像原理一、背景概述&ensp;&ensp;声波是一种机械波，能够在固体、流体或者气体中传播，广泛应用于声呐测距、工业探伤和医学影像等技术领域。超声成像作为一种非侵入性的医学影像技术，能够在疾病早期诊断，如形态学结构出现异常病变，血流动力学方面出现异常表现等方面提供参考信息，...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":603,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"超声成像","slug":"超声成像","count":2,"path":"api/categories/超声成像.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"超声物理","slug":"超声物理","count":2,"path":"api/tags/超声物理.json"}],"author":{"name":"Landdon","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/45172823/196003286-c2c4aa6e-a365-4492-ac64-aede8e18b244.jpeg","link":"/","description":"保持平和，持续进步 </br> </br> 一起加油！","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}}}